metadata.title: Fall Thansgiving Wine Bags - Thankful Blessed Themed Cotton linen Wine Gift Bag With Drawstring, Thansgiving Day Party Supplies Decorations, Autumn Gift for Friends, Besties, Colleagues (1 Pack)-03
features: 1) Each wine bag sizes 6.4" x 13.4", which can accommodate a regular 750ml wine bottle or all standard size wine bottles.
2) Our wine bags are made of cotton linen, and the cotton material makes the wine bags reusable and durable.
3) Wine Bag Care: Hand washing or machine washing.

4) Every cotton wine bag comes with a drawstring, which makes the bag easy to close and open, convenient for storage wine bottle or other items. Perfect for carrying wine bottle to celebration Thanksgiving party.

5) These bags are perfect for wrapping wine bottles size long or high. The burlap wine bottle bag is perfect for Thanksgiving parties, autumn parties and any other occasion, which is a perfect gift bag for dinners to celebrate and enjoy the happiness.
